      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARMATREE PASTA (4) has a strong overall record having seven wins and five places from 13 starts including a last start success (25.06) over 431m at this track. Has a good record at this journey. On top here on best form and expected to feature. GIVE A LITTLE (8) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten a nose, (24.84) at this track. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Expected to feature again. ARMATREE STRIPE (2) has mixed form recently, finishing eighth (26.08) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Well placed here and should do much better. ROSACKY RAYO (1) placed in impressive time last start - cannot be ignored.",
